    "text": [
        "Dear Sir,",
        "I am writing this letter to enquire about the United States tour, which school has planned for children and parents. Also I would like to express my interest in joining this trip and to offer my help for any admin related work require during the trip.",
        "I wonder if you could help me with duration and if any planned activity, so that I can prepare myself for this wonderful trip. I have seen on the internet it would be mostly rainy all the time, so I would like to know if you could provide us umbrella or rainy clothes or I have to shop it from the market.",
        "I was always excited to visit the United States, though due to some work engagement I was not able to make plan for this. so I would be more than happy to join school trip with my kids.",
        "Also, I have done volunteering to so many trips organised by our office, so I am excited if i get something to work in your trip.",
        "I am looking forward to hearing from you.",
        "Regards,",
        "Aman Kansal"
    ],
